description: The MSCI EMU Low Carbon SRI Selection Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap companies in the European Economic and Monetary Union (EMU) with high ESG characteristics and low carbon exposure, relative to their peers Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI EMU ESG UCITS ETF 1C
